{"tid":627681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【加埋69歲】洛賓、列貝利兩老續約拜仁","createTime":"2018-04-13T07:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T16:56:35.000Z","uid":5006,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"68e0933b7c61bfcb194ca31d4a2636676adce0a3","tid":627681,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180413/photo/bkn-20180413123520639-0413_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180413130720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180413123520639-0413_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180413130720&h=9536439a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜仁本季完成聯賽六連霸，奪得史上第28個德甲冠軍，而且剛又打入歐聯四強，可以話係大豐收。正所謂做生不如做熟，既然有成績，冇理由放棄原本強勁陣容，故球會決定同陣中兩老洛賓同列貝利續多一年約。 <br />\n洛賓、列貝利今年分別34同35歲，已步入職業生涯晚期，於球隊無疑出場機會減少，但最重要依然有貨交，本季合共上陣64場賽事，可謂屢建奇功。高層路明尼加表示，續約嘅底線係實際表現，而二人依然打出頂級足球，所以拜仁願意畀新約兩老。 <br />\n洛賓於09年加盟拜仁，迄今上陣286次射入138球；而列貝利07年來投，落場382次轟入117球。 <br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180413/photo/bkn-20180413123520639-0413_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180413130720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180413123520639-0413_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180413130720&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKW%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c61922ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180413/photo/bkn-20180413123520639-0413_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180413130720</a><br />\n<br />\n咁既年紀扭得又爆得又幾堅既<br />\n真係唔明點樣先keep到咁"},{"pid":"509ffd94a29b5279ac25c116da671eacad782965","tid":627681,"uid":133424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"2R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d49f05db34e2205247bdf47556d3ba29173235","tid":627681,"uid":80183,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"諗起賭俠1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\